items.preText: Tasmeem: "Soumya always falls over when playing shots away from his body. When he was on form (which was quite a long time ago), he pushing with his hands seemed to be no problem. Also he always had luck on his side with ball just evading fielders or falling in no man's land. But now that he is off colour, it's making him look like a sitting duck."
items.text: short outside off, Mushfiqur upper-cuts it towards deep backward point
items.postText: amzad: "personally i like the batting of Soumya and Liton, both of them remind me fearless Shahariar Hossain, Ashraful, Aftab and Tamim .All of them are/ were very talented, But except Tamim, none other can give good service to country. BCB should take immediate action to let this two guy know how important they are and how important their service for the team, specially Top 5 player of the team is nearly and above 30 now, they should take responsibility. "
